Package extended_mitre.cwe

Class CWEdetMethObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • extended_mitre.cwe.CWEdetMethObj
  • @Entity
public class CWEdetMethObj
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a CWE detection method object (method id attribute, method attribute, description attribute, effectiveness attribute, effectiveness notes attribute)

    Objects can be put into database

    It can create a CWE detection method object from given parameters and return it

    Author:
    Tomas Bozek (XarfNao)
